        <ul class="leftCol">
          <li><h3><a>Schedule A Viewing</a></h3>
            <div>
              <p>Pistilli makes finding your apartment convenient to your schedule. We offer an in house staff which is dedicated to leasing you the apartment from start to finish. If that isn’t enough, we have staff that can show you the apartments as well as the common areas at your convenience given you schedule an appointment. Our agents will help you get familiar in the area you wish to live in and walk you step-by-step through the application process.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="top: 47px;"><h3><a>Income Qualification</a></h3>
            <div>
              <p>Residents are required to have an annual income that is equal to 40 times the amount of the monthly rent. For example, if the rent is $1,500.00 a month, an applicant must document no less than $60,000.00 ($1,500.00 x 40). If the apartment has two applicants, the sum of both applicants will be considered.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="top: 94px;"><h3><a>Co-Signer Requirements</a></h3>
            <div>
              <p>If you are looking to have a guarantor co-sign, they must also apply and have a documented income equal to 60 times the monthly rent. The co-signer must reside in the United States.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="top: 141px;"><h3><a>Security Deposits</a></h3>
            <div>
              <p>The standard security deposit is one month’s rent. Additional security monies may be required if the management deems it necessary during the application process. Security deposits will earn interest subject to bank regulations. If you fulfill all the terms of your lease, the interest will be refunded minus a 1% administrative fee to which the owner is entitled.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="top: 188px;"><h3><a>Application Process</a></h3>
            <div>
              <p>An application can be approved and processed within 24 hours provided the applicant has the required documents. Once an application becomes fully approved, the lease must be signed within 72 hours.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="top: 235px;"><h3><a>Proper Documentation</a></h3>
            <div>
              <p>The following documentation is required for every applicant to be considered:</p>
              <ul id="considerations">
                <li>A completed application form</li>
                <li>$100.00 application fee.</li>
                <li>A complete copy of recent bank statements.</li>
                <li>A copy of photo ID</li>
                <li>An employment verification letter</li>
                <li>Three consecutive pay stubs</li>
                <li>Full income tax returns</li>
                <li>Landlord reference letter</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="top: 282px;"><h3><a>Required Payment At Lease Signing</a></h3>
            <div>
              <p>At the time of signing of your lease, you will need certified or bank checks only. A leasing agent will inform you via e-mail all details.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
